Line3.EDC7E: My boy…the young die and the old linger on. When will it end?
Line9.EDC7E: I want every spider in the barrens exterminated. I know not if they feel, if their queen would feel this same anguish if she lost her brood. Regardless, I want it done. Bring me their queen’s heart.
VoiceDir3.EDC7E: Tearful before composing herself. Then switches to bitter, cold hatred.
